{
  "id": "adv_event_2407_01_05",
  "title": "サニーピース\n号、出航！！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――無人島生活開始から、47時間経過",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――47 hours since deserted island life began",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 3.3200000107000003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 3.3200000107
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "タイムリミットまで残り1時間",
      "translations": {
        "en": "1 hour remaining until time limit",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.3200000107,
      "endTime": 5.580000019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "ついに……ついについに！\n五人乗りのいかだ、完成だよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Finally… finally!\nThe five-person raft is complete!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.7666666667,
      "endTime": 12.8286848704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "時間もなんとか間に合いそうね\n今から急いで海を渡ればギリギリゴール出来るわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looks like we'll just make it in time.\nIf we hurry and cross the sea now‚ we can barely reach the goal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.0333333333,
      "endTime": 19.6780045826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "予定より遅れたのは、私の提案のせいで\n作業が増えたからだよね……ごめんなさい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're behind schedule because my suggestion\nincreased the work… I'm sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.8666666667,
      "endTime": 27.840634981900003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "謝る必要はないわ\nおかげで私達らしい船になったじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's no need to apologize.\nThanks to that‚ it became a ship that's just like us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.0333333333,
      "endTime": 33.60526069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "キラキラして、可愛くて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sparkling and cute…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.8,
      "endTime": 36.666643953299996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "見てると笑顔になって元気がわいてくる\nサニーピースにぴったりの船だよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looking at it makes me smile and feel energized.\nIt's a ship perfect for Sunny Peace!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.8666666667,
      "endTime": 43.7328116099,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "海岸で拾った貝殻やシーグラスで\nいかだを飾り付けするなんて、よく思いついたわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Decorating the raft with shells and sea glass\npicked up from the beach― what a good idea.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.9333333333,
      "endTime": 50.6014058431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、飾り付けするのに手間はかかるし\nいかだも重くなるから、脱出の役には立たないんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But decorating takes effort\nand makes the raft heavier‚ so it doesn't help with escaping.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.8,
      "endTime": 59.9313150406,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことない……アイドルの衣装と同じ……\n衣装が素敵だとモチベーションが上がる……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not true… it's the same as idol costumes…\nWhen costumes are wonderful‚ motivation goes up…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.1333333333,
      "endTime": 66.4793652853,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "この船を見てると、やる気がもりもりわいてくるよ！\nこれならどんな大海原でも乗り越えられる気がする！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looking at this ship makes my motivation bubble up!\nI feel like we can overcome any ocean with this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.6666666667,
      "endTime": 75.5621990839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね……\n私もこの船を見てると、勇気がわいてくる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're right…\nLooking at this ship gives me courage too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.7666666667,
      "endTime": 81.8802266757,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "……千紗ちゃん\n出発する前にもう一度だけ聞かせて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Chisa-chan\nLet me ask one more time before we depart.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.0666666667,
      "endTime": 87.3091157596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "私は五人でゴールしたい……\nだから千紗ちゃん、私達と一緒に行かない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want all five of us to reach the goal…\nSo Chisa-chan‚ won't you come with us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.5,
      "endTime": 94.9347618104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "……実は、いかだ作りの合間に\n雫ちゃんに見てもらって海で泳ぐ練習をしたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Actually‚ during breaks from raft building‚\nI practiced swimming in the sea while Shizuku-chan watched.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.6333333333,
      "endTime": 105.0273465474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "サバイバル図鑑に載ってた頑丈な結び方で\nいかだが壊れないように補強もしたし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I reinforced the raft with the sturdy knots\nfrom the survival guide so it wouldn't break…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.2333333333,
      "endTime": 112.16589549369999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "スタッフさんにもお願いして\n特別に救命胴衣を貸してもらえることになって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I even asked the staff‚\nand they agreed to specially lend me a life jacket…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.3666666667,
      "endTime": 118.5962583224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "少しでも海が怖くなくなるように、思いついたことは\n全部やって……それでも、やっぱりまだ怖いけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Although I tried everything I could think of to make the sea\nfeel a little less scary… I'm still scared. But…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.8,
      "endTime": 129.8720184326,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "……勇気を出して、わがままを言うね\n私も、みんなと行きたい！　みんなと一緒がいい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'm going to be brave and say what I want.\nI want to go with everyone too! I want to be with everyone!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.0666666667,
      "endTime": 139.9346035639,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "迷惑をかけちゃうかもしれないけど\n私も一緒に行っていい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I might cause trouble‚ but\ncan I come along too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.1333333333,
      "endTime": 145.6648754438,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "昨日も言ったでしょ。千紗に迷惑をかけられたなんて\n思ったことは一度もないわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I told you yesterday. I've never once thought\nyou've caused me trouble.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.8666666667,
      "endTime": 152.6484352748,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
