      "text": "エアコン最高……ふかふかのソファ最高……\n好きなだけインターネット出来る……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Air conditioning is the best… fluffy sofa is the best…\nI can use the internet as much as I want…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.3666707357,
      "endTime": 190.1331557592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
