    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05-chs023.m4a",
      "text": "だって……私がオススメDVDの鑑賞会をやると\n怜ちゃんは真っ先にいなくなっちゃうし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because… whenever I have a DVD night with my picks‚\nyou're the first one to disappear…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 334.3666503907,
      "endTime": 342.1408000947,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05-chs024.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんは映画が好きじゃないのかなとか、私といても\n楽しくないのかなとか、いろいろ考えちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I kept thinking about things like whether you didn’t like movies…\nor whether you weren’t having fun being with me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 342.3333170574,
      "endTime": 351.4705277126,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "それは千紗に問題がある訳じゃなくて\n千紗の選ぶ映画に問題が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not because there's a problem with you‚\nbut with the movies you choose…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 351.6666503907,
      "endTime": 358.4676937104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
