      "text": "……いいわ。じゃあ、明日は二人で出かけましょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Fine. Then shall we go out together tomorrow?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 358.6666503907,
      "endTime": 363.2375802041,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05-chs025.m4a",
      "text": "え、いいの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ really?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 363.4333170574,
      "endTime": 365.6822286051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_05-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "千紗からデートに誘われて断る理由なんてないわよ",
      "translations": {
