      "text": "主人公がダンサー志望の女の人で、実力はあるのに\n周囲に認められなくて……気晴らしに友達に誘われて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The protagonist is a woman who dreams of becoming a dancer.\nAlthough she’s talented‚ no one around her acknowledges it.",
        "id": ""
